About this item

    This fits your .
  • Make sure this fits by entering your model number.
  • USB C HDMI Cable: This USB-C to HDMI cable is a convenient solution for connecting your USB-C device directly to your HDMI monitor, projector or TV, such as MacBook, Samsung S9, Dell XPS 15, etc. No Driver needed. Use the USB Type C HDMI cable cord to position your devices anywhere in your workspace as needed with less cable clutter.(NOTE: it is usb c cable not micro usb cable and does not support S7 S6 and other micro usb devices)
  • Broad Compatibility: The USB C HDMI Adapter Cable perfectly works with USB-C port computers with Mini DP / Thunderbolt 3.0 Alt mode such as Macbook 2017/2016, Macbook Pro, Samsung S10/S10 Plus/S9 / S9 / S8 Plus / Note 9 / Note 8, iMac 2017 (as host), Huawei Mate 10 / mate 10 pro, HTC 10, Dell XPS 13/15, Google Chromebook Pixel, and other USB C devices that support DP Alt Mode.
  • 4K 60Hz HDMI Cable: USB Type C to HDMI Cable supports video resolution up to 3840x2160 @ 60Hz(4K * 2K) and full HD 1080P @ 60Hz. The picture quality on a 4K @ 60Hz monitor or TV with the UHD resolution will astonish you. The thunderbolt 3 HDMI Cord also synchronously transmits audio and video signal, and supports mirror mode or extend mode.
  • Stable Signal Transmission: It is a handy USB C HDMI cable made of gold-plated connector and three layers of shielding, which provides improved corrosion and maximum durability, and can enhance signal transmission. The gold-plated plug on the thunderblot hdmi cord can fit well with the USB C port of your device.
  • Robust and Durable: Nylon Braided makes the cable flexible and resistant to wear, which can prevent cable from clutter and tearing. And the high quality gold plated contacts and metal case can prevent loose contact. The USB 3.1 Type C HDMI cable adapter can afford to plug and unplug more times.

Product Description

EASY for LARGER SCREEN VIEWING

  • UGREEN USB C HDMI Cable allows the laptop or mobile phone to be connected directly to a monitor, TV or projector to deliver the image. Leaving your phone as a computer, you can easily picture it from your cellphone to TV or other device.

4K 60HZ / THUNDERBOLT 3 SUPPORTED / DURABLE

  • The cable supports 4K @ 60Hz resolution, you can enjoy the larger and more immersive screen and picture quality. Nylon braided makes the cable flexible and resistant to wear, which can avoid cable clutter and tearing, so the cable can be durable.

Plug and Play, Easy to Use

  • Just plug and play directly, connect the laptop or phone to the monitor is a breeze, no external power, drivers or dongles required; The HDMI connector is gold-plated to provide rigidity; It is HDMI 1.4 Version, compatible with HDMI 2.0 and former version.

COMPREHENSIVE COMPATIBILITY

  • MacBook 2017 12 ", MacBook Pro 2017 13", Macbook 2016 12 "/ 13" / 15 "
  • MacBook Pro 2017 13 ", MacBook Pro 2017 13" / 15 "(Touch ID & Multi Touch Bar iMac 2017 21.5 "/ 27" (as a host computer)
  • Samsung Galaxy S10/ S10+/ S9 / S8 / S8 + / Note 10/ Note 9/ Note 8
  • Huawei P20 / Mate 10 Pro / Mate 10 / Matebook X/ Matebook X Pro
  • Dell XPS 13-9360 / 9350, XPS 15-9560, XPS 12-9250, XPS 13 2 IN 1, Inspiron 5000/7000, Inspiron Gaming 7000, AlienWare 13/15
  • Lenovo Miix 510, ThinkPad 13 (2017), Yoga 900
  • Acer Switch 3 / Acer Switch 5 / Acer Switch Alpha 12
  • Google ChromeBook Pixel (2015)
  • HP ENVY X360 15, ENVY 13 (2017), EliteBook folio G1
  • Oneplus 7 Pro

*Important Note*

  • It is not compatible with the devices that do not support the protocol of DP alt mode.
